                      <text>does not include a person who is a participatory security trustee in relation to the security if the person acts in the continuing administration or management of the scheme to which the security relates solely in the person's capacity as a participatory security trustee; and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </label-para>
            </amend>
